title: Aboriginal sites in Arthur-Pieman Conservation Area must be protected from 4WDs, court told
text: The Arthur-Pieman Conservation Area in Tasmania's north-west has culturally unique Aboriginal heritage that must be protected from vehicles, the Federal Court in Hobart hears. ...
